interactions.flavorLineOne: X没r doesn't have much to call his own, but he'll always have your gift. Until he eats them. If he does eat.

"The Nine watch you, Guardian. I do not know why, because nobody can know the Nine."

X没r spasms in an unpredictable cadence. A tentacle wafts out from his hood to float near you. Your skin hears its aroma.

By the time you process the sensation, an object has appeared in X没r's hand.

"I hand you this gift, but I am nothing, so know that it is of and from the Nine. Your acceptance is arbitrary."
